                </div>

                <div class="mt-5" style="border: 1px solid #AAA;">

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5">
                <h6 style="color: #333; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal;font-weight: 700; line-height: 150%; ">
                    Designed for Convenience
                </h6>
                <p class="blog-detail-para3 mt-4">
                    Our Bento Boxes are created to simplify catering without sacrificing quality.
                    No extra serving counters, no long queues, and no confusion—just neatly packed meals that keep
                    everything organized and efficient.<br /><br />

                    This makes them especially suitable for fast-paced environments where time and convenience matter.
                </p>
                <div style="border: 1px solid #AAA;">

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5">
                <h6 style="color: #333; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal;font-weight: 700; line-height: 150%; ">
                    A Thoughtful Way to Bring People Together
